{"tid":801110,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"屌那星 個00後同事唔撚識用火機","createTime":"2018-08-31T11:08:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-31T18:09:29.000Z","uid":104658,"like":14,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"23244e995094bef6e39363857b6d2e3beffdf3bb","tid":801110,"uid":104658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T11:08:33.000Z","msg":"是咁的，前排有個00後嚟返工&nbsp;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 見佢烚下烚下都算啦<br />\n<br />\n我哋成班同事諗住放假，買定料自己揸車去山bbq，本身都唔諗住叫佢 但佢又死都跟埋黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我哋分兩部車揸上山，點知條友無車都算&nbsp; 連車牌都無&nbsp; on99<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n間suv已經夠逼，仲要車埋佢 最後坐中間個dog seat 逼撚到仆街&nbsp;，我已經興過火屎<br />\n<br />\n一落車我哋圍內去打邊撈&nbsp;，叫個00後覇定爐起火&nbsp;，等我哋返黎<br />\n<br />\n扯完兩飛諗住返去食雞翼&nbsp;，去仲見個on9仔坐咗係到&nbsp;，係到研究緊支火機點用 話咩平時用開火槍&nbsp;，我槍佢老母<br />\n<br />\n之前我成程黑面&nbsp;&nbsp;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 燒到黑哂d腸丸就質哂比佢食<br />\n<br />\n最後襯佢去廁所痾尿&nbsp;，我哋成班揸車落山&nbsp;撇低佢&nbsp;，佢應該喊住咁行落山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53cce076d997e08e03f9069a164e3faa5951b597","tid":801110,"uid":104658,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T11:08:51.000Z","msg":"咁撚蠢"},{"pid":"32aefc759eda66375af0032133e9160c4d4f5a12","tid":801110,"uid":73750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"53cce076d997e08e03f9069a164e3faa5951b597","tid":801110,"uid":104658,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T11:08:51.000Z","msg":"咁撚蠢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T11:09:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0020f9550be20bbb695a4166e84dc0e6d05dcee1","tid":801110,"uid":89509,"like":23,"dislike":5,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T11:10:34.000Z","msg":"00後點會有車牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ca4f535261